creator: milamber@apache.org
text:
Bugzilla isn't a support forum, please send your questions on JMeter user mailing list.

Please note: Windows hide the suffix of known file like .bat. 
jmeter.bat is display as "jmeter" with type "Windows Batch File" on your desktop.
